node.text: Life hasn’t been too kind to me lately, so I stopped being kind to myself. It’s a bad habit that I have. My job is to motivate and inspire people but sometimes I find it hard to inspire myself. I’ll get so buried in things that I forget basic moments like taking time to breathe and stretch. Hopefully if you struggle with that too here’s a reminder to do some thing for yourself because you’re worth it. You can only take care of the people around you when you take care of yourself ❤️ @aloyoga

node.text:
So crazy how much my skin has changed the past couple weeks from this new routine. The skincare industry can be hard to navigate with how many products there are. For the past year I was using non-organic products with random oils in them that were causing my skin to break out with cystic acne. I stopped making videos without makeup because of how insecure I was. But we back! Thanks to @sonyadakar and all her organic products that changed my skin like crazy in just three weeks! I know it seems like a lot of product but they’re all super light and very clean so the combo is perfect! 
Use my code ‘Charly15’ for 15% off all products on her website till this Friday!

node.text: Defined brows, built up lashes, bronzed glow 🔮 creating these make up tutorials has been fun and something new. But remember you’re beautiful just the way you are and make up is just another way to express yourself 💜 this song actually really hits home for me, really listen to @alessiasmusic lyrics and what they’re talking about!
